# Docker Installation
Mac: [Docker Desktop for Mac](https://hub.docker.com/editions/community/docker-ce-desktop-mac)
Windows: [Docker Desktop for Windows](https://hub.docker.com/editions/community/docker-ce-desktop-windows)
Linux: 
```
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade
sudo apt install docker.io
sudo systemctl start docker
sudo systemctl enable docker
sudo systemctl status docker
```
:::spoiler 
**Installation Steps for Mac/Windows:**
1. Download Windows/Mac docker installable from above links.
2. Install dmg/exe files by following on-screen instructions and provide credentials If needed.

**Installation Steps for Linux Ubuntu:**
1. Execute above commands in Linux Terminal.
:::